De_tpoint is created within 2 Days for the ESL. I hope you like the updated version. I added complete new Buildings and a new Skybox. It should everything work. But keep in mind i will not change enything cause this is a closed Project for me. But if you want to change, you can. There is no decompiling "Blocker". But if you change something please give me the credits.

The Counter-Strike Map (Original) made by someone other. I don't know the Name of the Mapper.
Anyway, have fun with my newest creation. 

P.s. 2 Days are very short, so there are some effects missing. No HDR, Environment Sounds and Performance optimizings.
